'''Balka greens''' were a species of plant which grew on [[Arbra/Legends|Arbra]] during the time of the [[Arbran]] civilization. In the library of [[Grotto City]], [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] found an Arbran cookbook with a recipe requiring balka greens.<ref name="M67">[[Star Wars (1977) 67|''Star Wars'' (1977) 67]]</ref> Balka greens were among the vegetables that [[Russo Berlihat]] was instructed to feed to [[Moff/Legends|Moff]] [[Bandor (Moff)|Bandor's]] captive [[Protean]]; however, Berlihat himself was actually intended to be eaten by the shapeshifter.<ref name="SS">{{JournalCite|12|Shape-shifters}}</ref>

